All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class WebException
extends javax.servlet.ServletException

A simple exception to indicate web exceptions. If you throw this exception from anywhere in a servlet or JSP file, Tomcat will call the error.jsp page (see web.xml).
